Text: Discussion of ENA UpstreamPlease plan on attending the following meeting on ENA Upstream tomorrow from in EB If you cant attend please reply via email Thanks Yolanda

Pamela Sonnierbaby shower for Pam will be held Friday November in EB from to We will be serving cake and punch If you will be attending please RSVP to me by Tuesday October so that we can order an accurate amount of chairs for this event For those of you wanting to donate see me at least a day before the shower or sooner If you would like to buy your own gift she is registered at Babies R Us and Target If you have any questions please call me at Yolanda Pena
